text: Keramat Ali Tang. is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Mymensingh-5. ==Career== Tang was elected to parliament from Mymensingh-5 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Year of death unknown
title: Keramat Ali Tang.
